Only use 5 quart jug and 3 quart jug to get 4 quart.
Here is the solution which shows the water quantity in 3 jug.
     5 quart jug        3 quart jug   action
         5                   0        ->5
         2                   3        5->3
         2                   0        3->
         0                   2        5->3
         5                   2        ->5
         4                   3        5->3